    {
      "type": "thought",
      "text": "The user has shown a BSOD with the error code `WHEA_UNCORRECTABLE_ERROR`. This is a hardware-related error. Let me perform a proper enterprise root cause analysis.\n\nFirst, I need to:\n1. Research the WHEA_UNCORRECTABLE_ERROR2. Check system logs if possible\n3. Check for any dump files\n4. Research iFixit repairability scores\n5. Create diagnostic tools\n\nLet me start by checking the system for any relevant logs and dump files.",
