      "output": "\r\nProcessorNameString                       Identifier                            MaxClockSpeed CurrentClockSpeed\r\n-------------------                       ----------                            ------------- -----------------\r\nIntel(R) Core(TM) i5-7300HQ CPU @ 2.50GHz Intel64 Family 6 Model 158 Stepping 9                                \r\n\r\n\r\n",
