      "output": "\r\nName                     DriverVersion AdapterRAM Status\r\n----                     ------------- ---------- ------\r\nIntel(R) HD Graphics 630 31.0.101.2140 1073741824 OK    \r\nNVIDIA GeForce GTX 1050  31.0.15.3179  2147483648 OK    \r\n\r\n\r\n",
      "status": "success",
      "timestamp": 1783146295370
