ip install --upgrade pip\r\n    2. Install LibreHardwareMonitor for real-time temp monitoring\r\n    3. Check ADATA SSD firmware via ADATA SSD ToolBox\r\n    4. Update BIOS from HP support website\r\n    5. Consider repasting CPU if comfortable doing so\r\n    6. If crashes continue, test with matched RAM kit\r\n\r\n============================================================\r\nRun this script periodically to monitor system health.\r\nFor real-time monitoring, use LibreHardwareMonitor or HWiNFO64.\r\n============================================================\r\n",
