      "output": "Title: 2025 iFixit Translation Challenge Winners | Every Word Counts\nURL: https://www.ifixit.com/News/112330/the-words-that-fix-the-world-meet-our-2025-translation-challenge-winners\nPublished: 2026-06-07T10:32:50.000Z\nAuthor: Sandra Hiller\nHighlights:\nCelebrate the winners of iFixit's 2025 Translation Challenge—2411 guides translated in 7 languages. Join the mission to make repair global.\n\n---\n\nTitle: 🌍 Join the 2025 iFixit Translation Challenge\nURL: https://www.ifixit.com/News/109319/%F0%9F%8C%8D-join-the-2025-ifixit-translation-challenge\nPublished: 2026-06-12T15:05:59.000Z\nAuthor: Mariana Roca\nHighlights:\nFrom June 9 through July 31, join our 2025 Translation Challenge: translate iFixit content into your language, earn points, climb the ...\n\n---\n\nTitle: Community Contests - iFixit\nURL: https://www.ifixit.com/contests\nPublished: 2026-07-04T20:28:08.000Z\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\n# 2025 Translation Challenge\n...\nOur amazing linguists stepped up once again to translate guides and wikis, helping make repairs accessible to all. We selected 5 outstanding winners, with the top translator receiving a Pro Tech Toolkit! Plus, for each participant, we planted a tree in the iFixit forest on Tree-Nation. 🌱\n\n---\n\nTitle: Help us Translate and Win Prizes! - iFixit\nURL: https://www.ifixit.com/News/79160/help-us-translate-and-win-prizes\nPublished: 2026-06-17T12:10:57.000Z\nAuthor: Sandra Hiller\nHighlights:\nPrizes: · We'll be giving out one gift card worth $75 and · Two gift cards worth $50 and · Three gift cards worth $25 for your iFixit store.\n\n---\n\nTitle: Join Our 2024 Translation Challenge - iFixit\nURL: https://www.ifixit.com/News/94714/join-our-2024-translation-challenge-and-unlock-exciting-rewards\nPublished: 2026-05-14T16:38:03.000Z\nAuthor: Mariana Roca\nHighlights:\nSo, what are you waiting for? Join us in this exciting endeavor! Your translations help fixers worldwide and also unlock opportunities for fantastic prizes.\n...\n### Prizes:\n...\nWe’re excited to reward your efforts with these amazing prizes:\n...\n- One lucky winner will receive a ProTech Toolkit.\n- Two runners-up will each receive an iFixit Fast Charger.\n- Three participants will be awarded an Essential Electronics Toolkit.\n...\nPlease note that shipping restrictions may apply, limiting delivery to areas supported by our US and EU warehouses.If you are unable to receive a package from us in your area, we can exchange your prize equivalent for a donation to an iFixit-approved repair center of your choice.\n\n---\n\nTitle: Introducing Our 2024 Translation Challenge Winners! - iFixit\nURL: https://www.ifixit.com/News/102117/introducing-our-2024-translation-challenge-winners\nPublished: 2026-05-09T12:17:18.000Z\nAuthor: Mariana Roca\nHighlights:\nIntroducing Our 2024 Translation Challenge Winners! - iFixit\n...\nParticipants created 1,945 new guide translations!\n...\nwinners who’ve stood out through their incredible contributions.\n...\nWe’re blown away by the dedication of everyone who participated. Whether you translated one guide or a hundred, your contributions have empowered people to choose repair as their first option, helping to keep their devices out of landfills. It’s a huge step toward creating a more sustainable world!\n...\nAnd for every translator who didn’t win a prize, we’re showing our appreciation by planting a tree in your honor! Visit the iFixit forest on Tree Nation to check it out. Just like your translations, these trees will spread their branches, contributing to a better, greener world.\n...\nyou complete shows\n...\ndirectly on your profile\n...\njust the same\n...\nvisibility helps build\n...\nreputation grows, so do your abilities\n...\nthe platform.\n...\nThis challenge may be over, but your impact doesn’t have to stop here. You can contribute to translating repair guides and wikis all year round. You can even help to translate our entire user interface, making iFixit more accessible to a global audience.\n...\nIf you’re eager to take part in more challenges, head over to our contests page, where you’ll find exciting opportunities like the Repair Hero of the Year, which is still open for a few more weeks!\n\n---\n\nTitle: Translation Spotlight - iFixit\nURL: https://www.ifixit.com/News/85761/translation-spotlight\nPublished: 2026-06-21T16:23:52.000Z\nAuthor: Sandra Hiller\nHighlights:\nFor a duration of 2 months, we asked you to submit your translations and enter for a chance to win up to $75 credit in our store.\n\n---\n\nTitle: Happy International Translation Day! - iFixit\nURL: https://www.ifixit.com/News/83077/happy-international-translation-day\nPublished: 2026-05-21T06:21:08.000Z\nAuthor: Maria Parker\nHighlights:\nAnd just to give you a little bit of extra incentive: Until October 21—International Repair Day—you can participate in our Translation Challenge. Enter your translation(s) in this Google Form and you’re in for a chance to win a gift card for the iFixit Store. (And in case you are really not into screwdrivers, we also have some great t-shirts and other cool stuff in stock.)",
