      "output": "Title: iFixit Ambassador Team - The Fixer’s Guild\nURL: https://www.ifixit.com/ambassadors\nPublished: 2026-05-10T13:00:57.000Z\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nAs an ambassador, you'll have the chance to: · Test and review iFixit products · Create engaging content through videos, photos, and blogs · Advocate for the Right ...\n\n---\n\nTitle: Spread the repair culture with the iFixit Street Team!\nURL: https://www.ifixit.com/en-ifixit-street-team\nPublished: 2026-06-08T19:04:39.000Z\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\n# What’s In It for You?\n...\n- Fair compensation plus travel cost coverage\n- Access to iFixit tools & materials\n- Free merch (T-shirt, stickers, posters)\n- Regular support and collaboration\n- Gain public speaking experience\n\n---\n\nTitle: Jobs at iFixit USA San Luis Obispo, CA and Chattanooga, TN\nURL: https://www.ifixit.com/about-us/careers/jobs-usa\nPublished: 2026-06-11T21:31:33.000Z\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\n# Benefits & Perks\n...\nFull benefits package. Competitive medical, dental, vision and life insurance with generous employer contribution. Plus a stipend toward coverage for your dependent(s).\n...\nDirectly reap the benefits of all your hard work. We offer full-time employees a 401k plan with a 4% employer match.\n...\niFixit supports flexible vacation time and offers a number of paid holidays, so you can maintain a sustainable work-life balance.\n...\nFull-time employees have access to a Dependent Care FSA. Take some of the pressure off of finding childcare!\n...\nWe provide company lunches every Tuesday and Thursday made by our in-house chefs. And we also have communal snacks and drinks for you to grab at any time.\n...\nWe also offer generous stipends towards repair and wellness, headphones, and a bike/alternative mode of transportation for all employees.\n\n---\n\nTitle: iFixit GmbH Average Salary, Pay Ranges & Benefits | Salary.com\nURL: https://www.salary.com/research/company/ifixit-gmbh-salary\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: Site built by: Salary.com\nHighlights:\nData Updated: June, 2026\n...\nAs of June 2026, the average annual salary for employees at iFixit GmbH in the United States is $104,341. This translates to an approximate hourly wage of $50. Salaries at iFixit GmbH typically range from $91,874 to $117,854 annually, reflecting the diverse roles and experience levels within the company.\n...\nConsidering a career at iFixit GmbH? Explore authentic employee reviews to learn about the work environment, career growth opportunities, pay transparency and benefits. These first-hand insights can help you set realistic compensation expectations and make informed career decisions.\n...\nand there are\n...\nis good, and advancement opportunities\n...\nwho seek them\n...\nBenefits are above average.\n...\ncompany adapts well\n...\n## What Benefits Does iFixit GmbH Offer Beyond Salary?\n...\nA competitive compensation package is more than just a salary. iFixit GmbH offers a comprehensive benefits package designed to support your health, financial future, and overall well-being. Below are the most common key benefits:\n...\n401(K)\n...\nTime Off (days)\n...\n### 1. What is the average salary for employees at iFixit GmbH?\n...\nThe average annual total compensation for employees at iFixit GmbH is approximately $104,341. However, this is an aggregate figure, actual salaries can range significantly, typically from $91,874 to $117,854, depending on factors like job role, experience, and location.\n...\nThe average annual salary at iFixit GmbH is $104,341, or an hourly wage of $50, in comparison to Gyrus which pays $125,162 per year or $60 per hour.\n...\ncost-of\n...\nfor different locations rather\n...\nas a separate, itemized\n...\nfor roles in high-cost\n...\nset higher to account for these\n...\nMost companies, likely including iFixit GmbH, conduct formal salary reviews annually, often tied to performance evaluations. During these reviews, factors like individual performance, meeting goals, company performance, and market adjustments are typically considered for potential salary increases.\n\n---\n\nTitle: iFixit GmbH Hourly Pay Rate & Wages | Salary.com\nURL: https://www.salary.com/research/company/hourly-wage-for-ifixit-gmbh\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: Site built by: Salary.com\nHighlights:\nData Updated: June, 2026\n...\nAs of June 2026, the average hourly salary for employees at iFixit GmbH in the United States is $50. This translates to an approximate annual wage of $104,341. Salaries at iFixit GmbH typically range from $44 to $57 hourly, reflecting the diverse roles and experience levels within the company.\n...\nConsidering a career at iFixit GmbH? Explore authentic employee reviews to learn about the work environment, career growth opportunities, pay transparency and benefits. These first-hand insights can help you set realistic compensation expectations and make informed career decisions.\n...\n## What Benefits Does iFixit GmbH Offer Beyond Salary?\n...\nA competitive compensation package is more than just a salary. iFixit GmbH offers a comprehensive benefits package designed to support your health, financial future, and overall well-being. Below are the most common key benefits:\n...\n401(K)\n...\nTime Off (days)\n...\nIFixit GmbH pays its employees an average of $50 per hour. The average salary at iFixit GmbH range from $44 to $57 per hour. It's important to remember that these are overall averages, actual salaries vary significantly based on specific job titles, years of experience, skills, and location.\n...\nThe salary at iFixit GmbH is lesser than the similar company. The average annual salary at iFixit GmbH is $104,341, or an hourly wage of $50, in comparison to Gyrus which pays $125,162 per year or $60 per hour.\n...\nA Managing Director at iFixit GmbH typically earns an average hourly base salary of around $388, with a general range of $297 to $489.\n...\n### 6. What kind of benefits does iFixit GmbH typically offer employees?\n...\nIFixit GmbH generally offers a range of employee benefits designed to support their workforce's health, financial well-being, and work-life balance. Comprehensive health insurance (medical, dental, vision), a 401(k) retirement savings plan (often with a company match), paid time off (PTO), and potentially disability and life insurance are included. For a more detailed list of benefits, please see our \"Employee Benefits at iFixit GmbH\" section on this page.\n\n---\n\nTitle: iFixit is hiring: PR Coordinator in Chattanooga\nURL: https://www.mediabistro.com/jobs/856966064-ifixit-is-hiring-pr-coordinator-in-chattanooga\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\n* Organization and attention to detail.### **iFixit is an awesome place to work. Here are some of our perks:**\n...\n* Work laptop, and any software you need.\n* 401k plan with 4% employer match.\n...\n* Full benefits package. Competitive medical, dental, vision and life insurance with generous employer contribution. Plus a stipend toward coverage for your dependent(s).\n...\n* Company paid short term disability.\n...\n* Generous stipends towards repair & wellness.\n...\n* $400 towards a bike or alternative method of transportation.\n...\n* A sweet pair of headphones to get your head in the game.\n...\n* Employee discounts on parts and tools.\n...\n* Charitable contribution matching! We'll 100% match your contribution, tax deductible.### **Background on iFixit**\n\n---\n\nTitle: Assembly Associate Job Opening in Chattanooga, TN at iFixit | Career.com\nURL: https://www.career.com/job/ifixit/assembly-associate/j202604110248047877529\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: Site built by: Career.com\nHighlights:\niFixit is an awesome place to work. Here are some of our perks:\n...\n- A career where you will be actively working to make the world better.\n- A repairable laptop, and any software you need.\n- Full benefits package. Competitive medical, dental, vision and life insurance with generous employer contribution. Plus a stipend toward coverage for your dependent(s).\n- 401k plan with 4% employer match.\n- Flexible vacation time paid holidays.\n- Dependent Care FSA.\n- Generous stipends towards repair & wellness.\n- $400 towards a bike or alternative method of transportation.\n- A sweet pair of headphones to get your head in the game.\n- Team member discounts on parts and tools.\n- Charitable contribution matching! We'll 100% match your tax deductible contribution.\n...\nSalary : $12 - $50,000\n...\nIf your compensation planning software is too rigid to deploy winning incentive strategies, it’s time to find an adaptable solution. Compensation Planning\n...\norganization's compensation strategy with salary data sets that HR and team managers can use to pay your staff right. Surveys & Data Sets\n...\nEmployees: Get a Salary Increase Apply for this job and sign up for alerts\n\n---\n\nTitle: We’re Hiring: Be an iFixit Video Host!\nURL: https://www.ifixit.com/News/3925/be-an-ifixit-video-host\nPublished: 2026-06-25T03:54:10.000Z\nAuthor: Matt Barnes\nHighlights:\nWe’re Hiring: Be an iFixit Video Host!\n...\n5% Off\n...\nHi, it’s me MJ with iFixit, and today I have an exciting announcement. Have you ever watched our YouTube channel and thought, “I can totally do MJ’s job?” Well, now’s your chance! We’re looking to add another host to our video team, so if you’re into technology, love the DIY repair community, and are super comfortable talking to tons of strangers on camera, we want to hear from you.\n...\nWe’re looking for someone who is passionate about our mission. Though we’re best-known for our gadget teardowns, why we do what we do extends far beyond that. It’s our mission to empower people to repair everything, and this goal has global ramifications. The repair manuals we publish for free have helped millions of people repair their gadgets—and that saves them tons of money, and slows the cycle of consumption. We love that.\n...\nSo, if you get riled up by unsustainable design and the global impact of consumption, toss your hat in the ring as an advocate, and apply for this position. The position is located in San Luis Obispo, California (that’s where our office and recording studio is). Check out the job posting. If you think you’d be a good fit, shoot a short video introducing yourself to us, and let us know why you want to join our team. When you’re done, send a link to your video and your resume to videohost@ifixit.com.",
